---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section id="pricing" class="py-24 bg-dark-accent relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="pricing-bg absolute inset-0" style={`background-image: url('${base}/bg/pricing-bg.webp')`}></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4 reveal-scale">
      <span class="gradient-text">料金について</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-400 mb-16 reveal">Pricing</p>

    <div class="bg-dark-bg rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-gray-700 reveal hover:border-steel-blue/50 transition-colors duration-300">
      <p class="text-lg text-center mb-8">
        図面の種類・物量に応じて個別にお見積りいたします。<br>
        お気軽にお問い合わせください。
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-gray-700">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xl font-medium text-white">一般建築金物 製作図</p>
            <p class="text-gray-400">A1 / A2 サイズ</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-metallic-gold">¥9,000<span class="text-base text-gray-400">〜/枚</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-gray-700">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xl font-medium text-white">アルミ既製品 納まり図</p>
            <p class="text-gray-400">A1 / A2 サイズ</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-metallic-gold">¥4,500<span class="text-base text-gray-400">〜/枚</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-dark-accent rounded-lg">
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-steel-blue mr-2">※</span>
            複雑な図面・特殊仕様の場合は別途ご相談
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-steel-blue mr-2">※</span>
            物量によるボリュームディスカウントあり
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-12 reveal">
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-steel-blue hover:bg-steel-light text-white font-medium rounded transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(74,111,165,0.4)]">
        お見積り依頼 →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.pricing-bg {
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  opacity: 0.1;
  filter: brightness(0.4);
}
</style>
